<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>鸣潮体力推送</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-color: #0f1222;
      --card-bg: #161a2f;
      --accent-color: #f6d15e;
      --text-main: #eaeaea;
      --text-sub: #9aa3c1;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--text-main);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: var(--accent-color);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .intro {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .info-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 16px 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .info-item {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    .label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .value {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .image-container {
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding-top: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>鸣潮体力推送</h2>
    <div class="intro">
      漂泊者您好，您的体力已达到设定的推送阈值，请及时上线。
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-list">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">UID</span>
        <span class="value">{{uid}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">当前体力</span>
        <span class="value">{{stamina}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item" style="grid-column: span 2;">
        <span class="label">推送阈值</span>
        <span class="value">{{threshold}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{stamina_image}}" alt="stamina" />
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      如需关闭推送，请向机器人发送相应指令。
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>